name: flowerpower
description: @sianvictoriauk - Originally a photograph I took of flowers on the 2nd August 2006. The image was mirrored and inverted using old-school photosuite vista software that came with a Vivitar camera at the time. The creation was part of my 'Flashcore x photography'. A collection I made at age 15 but never shared. Today, 24/05/21 I've recovered it from a CD to finally get seen.
